      "text": "Skip to main content\nSkip to toolbar\n\nDashboard\nHome\nUpdates\n\nPosts\nAll Posts\nAdd Post\nCategories\nTags\n\nMedia\nLibrary\nAdd Media File\n\nPages\nAll Pages\nAdd Page\n\nComments\n\nAppearance\nThemes\nEditor\nFonts\n\nPlugins\nInstalled Plugins\nAdd Plugin\n\nUsers\nAll Users\nAdd User\nProfile\n\nTools\nAvailable Tools\nImport\nExport\nSite Health\nExport Personal Data\nErase Personal Data\nTheme File Editor\nPlugin File Editor\n\nSettings\nGeneral\nConnectors\nWriting\nReading\nDiscussion\nMedia\nPermalinks\nPrivacy\nCollapse Menu\nAbout WordPress\nMy WordPress Website\nCtrl+K\nOpen command palette\n0\n0 Comments in moderation\nNew\nHowdy, admin\nScreen Options\nHelp\nDashboard\nDismiss\nWelcome to WordPress!\n\nLearn more about the 7.0 version.\n\nAuthor rich content with blocks and patterns\n\nBlock patterns are pre-configured block layouts. Use them to get inspired or create new pages in a flash.\n\nAdd a new page\nCustomize your entire site with block themes\n\nDesign everything on your site — from the header down to the footer, all using blocks and patterns.\n\nOpen site editor\nSwitch up your site’s look & feel with Styles\n\nTweak your site, or give it a whole new look! Get creative — how about a new color palette or font?\n\nEdit styles\nSite Health Status\nMove up\nMove down\nToggle panel: Site Health Status\nNo information yet…\n\nSite health checks will automatically run periodically to gather information about your site. You can also visit the Site Health screen to gather information about your site now.\n\nAt a Glance\nMove up\nMove down\nToggle panel: At a Glance\n1 Published post\n2 Published pages\n1 Comment\n\nWordPress 7.0 running Twenty Twenty-Five theme.\n\nActivity\nMove up\nMove down\nToggle panel: Activity\nRecently Published\nMay 20th, 5:46 pm\nHello world!\nRecent Comments\n\nFrom A WordPress Commenter on Hello world!\n\nHi, this is a comment. To get started with moderating, editing, and deleting comments, please visit the Comments screen in…\n\nUnapprove | Reply | Edit | Spam | Trash | View\n\nView more comments\nAll (1) | Mine (0) | Pending (0) | Approved (1) | Spam (0) | Trash (0)\nQuick Draft\nMove up\nMove down\nToggle panel:\nQuick Draft\nTitle \nContent \n\nWordPress Events and News\nMove up\nMove down\nToggle panel: WordPress Events and News\n\nAttend an upcoming event near you.  Select location\n\n\t\nWordCamp Europe 2026\nWordCamp  Krakow, Poland\nJune 4–6, 2026\n\t\nWordUp Wrocław - spotkanie społeczności WordPressa\nMeetup  Wrocław, Poland\nThursday, Jun 11, 2026\n6:00 pm GMT+2\nWant more events? Help organize the next one!\nWordPress 7.0 “Armstrong”\nWordPress 7.0 Release Candidate 4\nOpen Channels FM: Artificial [fill in the blank]\nWordPress.org blog: WordPress 7.0 “Armstrong”\nWPTavern: #217 – Leonardo Losovic on Affordable and Accurate WordPress Translations Using AI\n\nMeetups \n(opens in a new tab)\n | WordCamps \n(opens in a new tab)\n | News \n(opens in a new tab)\n\nThank you for creating with WordPress.\n\nVersion 7.0",
